<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA42">
<l>nērntaravaṅ koḷḷac ciṟukiṟṟō nīyataṉai</l>
<l>yīrntaḷavē koṇṭicaiya vaittāyō - pērntu</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkuḻavit tāyvaḷara māṭṭātō veṉṉō</l>
<l>viḷaṅkuḻavit tiṅka ḷitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did it shrink when it was seized [and] taken by the snake? Did you</l>
<l>saw [and] place it to be fit, having taken the measure? Again,</l>
<l>as one with a fertile childhood, will it not be able to grow, why,</l>
<l>this, the young child moon?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
